;\">+</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">[</span>i <span class=\"token operator\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 204, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">-</span><span class=\"token number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 145, 87); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-style: italic !important; font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">//前缀和运算</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"token function\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(102, 153, 204); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">(</span><span class=\"token string\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 204, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">&quot;%d &quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">,</span> a<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">;</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">}</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"token keyword\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(204, 153, 204); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(249, 145, 87); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">;</span>\n &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: normal !important; line-height: normal !important;\">}</span></code><p><span class=\"token punctuation\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-variant-ligatures: normal !important; font-variant-numeric: normal !important; font-variant-east-asian: normal !important; font-stretch: no