k-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-meta-i-c  md-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a class=\"md-inner-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E9%9B%86%E7%BE%A4%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84-session-%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: rgb(224, 224, 224); -webkit-user-drag: none;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">二、集群下的 Session 管理</span></a></span></p></li></ul></ul><h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.63rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.875rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">一、负载均衡</span></h2><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">集群中的应用服务器（节点）通常被设计成无状态，用户可以请求任何一个节点。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">负载均衡器会根据集群中每个节点的负载情况，将用户请求转发到合适的节点上。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">负载均衡器可以用来实现高可用以及伸缩性：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">高可用：当某个节点故障时，负载均衡器会将用户请求转发到另外的节点上，从而保证所有服务持续可用；</span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">伸缩性：根据系统整体负载情况，可以很容易地添加或移除节点。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">负载均衡器运行过程包含两个部分：</span></p><ol class=\"ol-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.875rem; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif; white-space: normal;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">根据负载均衡算法得到转发的节点；</span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">进行转发。</span></p></li></ol><h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.17rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">负载均衡算法</span></h3><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1. 轮询（Round Robin）</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">轮询算法把每个请求轮流发送到每个服务器上。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">下图中，一共有 6 个客户端产生了 6 个请求，这 6 个请求按 (1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6) 的顺序发送。(1, 3, 5) 的请求会被发送到服务器 1，(2, 4, 6) 的请求会被发送到服务器 2。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/9daa3616-00a4-48c4-9146-792dc8499be3.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">该算法比较适合每个服务器的性能差不多的场景，如果有性能存在差异的情况下，那么性能较差的服务器可能无法承担过大的负载（下图的 Server 2）。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/bfea8772-d01b-4a51-8adc-edfd7d3dce84.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2. 加权轮询（Weighted Round Robbin）</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">加权轮询是在轮询的基础上，根据服务器的性能差异，为服务器赋予一定的权值，性能高的服务器分配更高的权值。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">例如下图中，服务器 1 被赋予的权值为 5，服务器 2 被赋予的权值为 1，那么 (1, 2, 3, 4, 5) 请求会被发送到服务器 1，(6) 请求会被发送到服务器 2。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/4ab87717-e264-4232-825d-8aaf08f14e8b.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3. 最少连接（least Connections）</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">由于每个请求的连接时间不一样，使用轮询或者加权轮询算法的话，可能会让一台服务器当前连接数过大，而另一台服务器的连接过小，造成负载不均衡。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">例如下图中，(1, 3, 5) 请求会被发送到服务器 1，但是 (1, 3) 很快就断开连接，此时只有 (5) 请求连接服务器 1；(2, 4, 6) 请求被发送到服务器 2，只有 (2) 的连接断开，此时 (6, 4) 请求连接服务器 2。该系统继续运行时，服务器 2 会承担过大的负载。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/e98deb5a-d5d4-4294-aa9b-9220d4483403.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">最少连接算法就是将请求发送给当前最少连接数的服务器上。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">例如下图中，服务器 1 当前连接数最小，那么新到来的请求 6 就会被发送到服务器 1 上。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/43d323ac-9f07-4e4a-a315-4eaf8c38766c.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4. 加权最少连接（Weighted Least Connection）</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在最少连接的基础上，根据服务器的性能为每台服务器分配权重，再根据权重计算出每台服务器能处理的连接数。</span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">5. 随机算法（Random）</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">把请求随机发送到服务器上。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">和轮询算法类似，该算法比较适合服务器性能差不多的场景。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/a42ad3a7-3574-4c48-a783-ed3d08a0688a.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">6. 源地址哈希法 (IP Hash)</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">源地址哈希通过对客户端 IP 计算哈希值之后，再对服务器数量取模得到目标服务器的序号。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">可以保证同一 IP 的客户端的请求会转发到同一台服务器上，用来实现会话粘滞（Sticky Session）</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/0f399a9f-1351-4b2d-b8a4-2ebe82b1a703.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.17rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">转发实现</span></h3><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1. HTTP 重定向</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">HTTP 重定向负载均衡服务器使用某种负载均衡算法计算得到服务器的 IP 地址之后，将该地址写入 HTTP 重定向报文中，状态码为 302。客户端收到重定向报文之后，需要重新向服务器发起请求。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">需要两次请求，因此访问延迟比较高；</span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">HTTP 负载均衡器处理能力有限，会限制集群的规模。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">该负载均衡转发的缺点比较明显，实际场景中很少使用它。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/02a1fbfd-7a9d-4114-95df-ca2445587a1f.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2. DNS 域名解析</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在 DNS 解析域名的同时使用负载均衡算法计算服务器 IP 地址。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">优点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">DNS 能够根据地理位置进行域名解析，返回离用户最近的服务器 IP 地址。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">由于 DNS 具有多级结构，每一级的域名记录都可能被缓存，当下线一台服务器需要修改 DNS 记录时，需要过很长一段时间才能生效。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">大型网站基本使用了 DNS 做为第一级负载均衡手段，然后在内部使用其它方式做第二级负载均衡。也就是说，域名解析的结果为内部的负载均衡服务器 IP 地址。</span></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"500px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/d2c072cc-8b17-480c-813e-18cdb3b4b51f.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3. 反向代理服务器</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">反向代理服务器位于源服务器前面，用户的请求需要先经过反向代理服务器才能到达源服务器。反向代理可以用来进行缓存、日志记录等，同时也可以用来做为负载均衡服务器。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在这种负载均衡转发方式下，客户端不直接请求源服务器，因此源服务器不需要外部 IP 地址，而反向代理需要配置内部和外部两套 IP 地址。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">优点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">与其它功能集成在一起，部署简单。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">所有请求和响应都需要经过反向代理服务器，它可能会成为性能瓶颈。</span></p></li></ul><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4. 网络层</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在操作系统内核进程获取网络数据包，根据负载均衡算法计算源服务器的 IP 地址，并修改请求数据包的目的 IP 地址，最后进行转发。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">源服务器返回的响应也需要经过负载均衡服务器，通常是让负载均衡服务器同时作为集群的网关服务器来实现。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">优点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在内核进程中进行处理，性能比较高。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">和反向代理一样，所有的请求和响应都经过负载均衡服务器，会成为性能瓶颈。</span></p></li></ul><h4 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.12rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: white; line-height: 1.375rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">5. 链路层</span></h4><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在链路层根据负载均衡算法计算源服务器的 MAC 地址，并修改请求数据包的目的 MAC 地址，并进行转发。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">通过配置源服务器的虚拟 IP 地址和负载均衡服务器的 IP 地址一致，从而不需要修改 IP 地址就可以进行转发。也正因为 IP 地址一样，所以源服务器的响应不需要转发回负载均衡服务器，可以直接转发给客户端，避免了负载均衡服务器的成为瓶颈。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">这是一种三角传输模式，被称为直接路由。对于提供下载和视频服务的网站来说，直接路由避免了大量的网络传输数据经过负载均衡服务器。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">这是目前大型网站使用最广负载均衡转发方式，在 Linux 平台可以使用的负载均衡服务器为 LVS（Linux Virtual Server）。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">参考：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-meta-i-c  md-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.jscape.com/blog/load-balancing-algorithms\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: rgb(224, 224, 224); -webkit-user-drag: none;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Comparing Load Balancing Algorithms</span></a></span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-meta-i-c  md-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://slideplayer.com/slide/6599069/#\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: rgb(224, 224, 224); -webkit-user-drag: none;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Redirection and Load Balancing</span></a></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.63rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.875rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">二、集群下的 Session 管理</span></h2><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">一个用户的 Session 信息如果存储在一个服务器上，那么当负载均衡器把用户的下一个请求转发到另一个服务器，由于服务器没有用户的 Session 信息，那么该用户就需要重新进行登录等操作。</span></p><h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.17rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Sticky Session</span></h3><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">需要配置负载均衡器，使得一个用户的所有请求都路由到同一个服务器，这样就可以把用户的 Session 存放在该服务器中。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">当服务器宕机时，将丢失该服务器上的所有 Session。</span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"400px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/1623f524-b011-40c8-b83f-eab38d538f76.png\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.17rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Session Replication</span></h3><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">在服务器之间进行 Session 同步操作，每个服务器都有所有用户的 Session 信息，因此用户可以向任何一个服务器进行请求。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">占用过多内存；</span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">同步过程占用网络带宽以及服务器处理器时间。</span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"400px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/40c6570d-c1d7-4c38-843e-ba991b2328c2.png\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><h3 class=\"md-end-block md-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; break-after: avoid-page; break-inside: avoid; orphans: 4; font-size: 1.17rem; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; font-family: &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, Corbel, sans-serif; clear: both; overflow-wrap: break-word; padding: 0px; color: rgb(222, 222, 222); line-height: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Session Server</span></h3><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">使用一个单独的服务器存储 Session 数据，可以使用传统的 MySQL，也使用 Redis 或者 Memcached 这种内存型数据库。</span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">优点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">为了使得大型网站具有伸缩性，集群中的应用服务器通常需要保持无状态，那么应用服务器不能存储用户的会话信息。Session Server 将用户的会话信息单独进行存储，从而保证了应用服务器的无状态。</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">缺点：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">需要去实现存取 Session 的代码。</span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600px\" src=\"https://cs-notes-1256109796.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/fdc45a09-f838-4348-8959-d2c793727788.png\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; position: absolute;\"></span></p><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(184, 191, 198); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">参考：</span></p><ul class=\"ul-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: square;\"><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p class=\"md-end-block md-p\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;\"><span class=\"md-meta-i-c  md-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"https://sivalabs.in/2018/02/session-management-using-spring-session-jdbc-datastore/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out 0s; color: rgb(224, 224, 224); -webkit-user-drag: none;\"><span class=\"md-plain\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Session Management using Spring Session with JDBC DataStore</span></a></span></p></li><li class=\"md-\" style=\"\"><p><br/></p></li></ul><p><br/></p>', '西班牙', '2022-06-07 01:05:01', 0, 0, 1, 1);
INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (123, 44, 'Java', 'SpringBoot集成Mybatis-Plus及Mybatis-Plus简单操作', '<p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">## </span><span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;font-weight: bold;\">一、SpringBoot集成Mybatis-Plus方法</span></p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">1.</span> 创建springboot项目</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;![<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">image-20220427222337290</span>](<span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/weiyuexin/blogimg@latest/img/202204272223414.png</span>)</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;这里可以选择MySQL坐标，也可以不选然后自己手动添加</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;![<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">image-20220427222500038</span>](<span style=\"text-decoration-line: underline;\">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/weiyuexin/blogimg@latest/img/202204272225102.png</span>)</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">2.</span> 添加依赖</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!--mybatis-plus--&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;com.baomidou&lt;/groupId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;mybatis-plus-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;version&gt;3.5.0&lt;/version&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!--MySQL依赖--&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;mysql&lt;/groupId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;mysql-connector-java&lt;/artifactId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;runtime&lt;/scope&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!--druid--&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;com.alibaba&lt;/groupId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;druid-spring-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;version&gt;1.2.9&lt;/version&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;!--lombok--&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.projectlombok&lt;/groupId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;lombok&lt;/artifactId&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/dependency&gt;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">3.</span> 在application.yml中配置数据库</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;server:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;port: 8080</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;servlet:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;context-path: /</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;spring:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;datasource:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;druid: &nbsp; #数据源使用druid</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;driver-class-name: com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;url: jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/ssm_db?useUnicode=true&amp;characterEncoding=UTF-8&amp;useJDBC49CompliantTimezoneShift=true&amp;useLegacyDatetimeCode=false&amp;serverTimezone=GMT%2B8</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;username: root</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;password: root</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">4.</span> 使用Lombok创建实体类</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Book实体类:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;@Data</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;public class Book {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;private Integer id;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;private String type;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;private String name;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;private String description;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;}</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">5.</span> 使用Mybatis-Plus创建dao层方法</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;使用继承 <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`BaseMapper&lt;实体类&gt;`</span>的方法，mp帮我们就创建了常用的sql</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;import com.baomidou.mybatisplus.core.mapper.BaseMapper;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;import com.example.domain.Book;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;import org.apache.ibatis.annotations.Mapper;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;@Mapper</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;public interface BookMapper extends BaseMapper&lt;Book&gt; {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;}</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #6796e6;\">6.</span> 附：使用到的数据库的创建语句：</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```sql</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> NAMES utf8mb4;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">0</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">-- ----------------------------</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">-- Table structure for book</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">-- ----------------------------</span></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">DROP</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">TABLE</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">IF</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">EXISTS</span> <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`book`</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">CREATE</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">TABLE</span> <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`book`</span> &nbsp;(</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`id`</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">int</span>(<span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">0</span>) <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NOT</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NULL</span> AUTO_INCREMENT,</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`type`</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">varchar</span>(<span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">255</span>) <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">CHARACTER</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> utf8 <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">COLLATE</span> utf8_general_ci <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NOT</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NULL</span>,</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`name`</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">varchar</span>(<span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">255</span>) <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">CHARACTER</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> utf8 <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">COLLATE</span> utf8_general_ci <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NOT</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NULL</span>,</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`description`</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">varchar</span>(<span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">255</span>) <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">CHARACTER</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> utf8 <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">COLLATE</span> utf8_general_ci <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NOT</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">NULL</span>,</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">PRIMARY</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">KEY</span> (<span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">`id`</span>) <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">USING</span> BTREE</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;) ENGINE <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">739889170</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">CHARACTER</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> utf8 <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">COLLATE</span> <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> utf8_general_ci ROW_FORMAT <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Dynamic</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">SET</span> FOREIGN_KEY_CHECKS <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #b5cea8;\">1</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;```</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">## </span><span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;font-weight: bold;\">二、测试增删改查</span></p><p><br/></p><p>```</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Autowired</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; private BookMapper bookMapper;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; //测试查询</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Test</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; void testGetById(){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; System.out.println(bookMapper.selectById(3));</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; //测试查询所有</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Test</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; void testGetAll(){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; System.out.println(bookMapper.selectList(null));</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; //测试保存</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Test</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; void testSave(){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Book book = new Book();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; book.setName(&quot;汤家凤2023考研高数辅导书&quot;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; book.setType(&quot;考研&quot;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; book.setDescription(&quot;2023考研高数汤家凤&quot;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bookMapper.insert(book);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; //测试修改</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Test</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; void testUpdate(){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Book book = new Book();</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; book.setId(739889166);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; book.setType(&quot;数学&quot;);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bookMapper.updateById(book);</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; //测试删除</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @Test</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; void testDelete(){</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; bookMapper.deleteById(739889166);</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p><p>```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">## </span><span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;font-weight: bold;\">三、配置使用数据库默认id自增策略</span></p><p><br/></p><p>mybatis-plus执行时对于id的处理默认是使用雪花算法随机生成id，但是我们在数据库表中给id设置的是自增（没有生效），设置默认使用数据库id自增策略的方式有两种</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">**1.在application.yml配置文件中配置：**</span></p><p><br/></p><p>```yaml</p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">mybatis-plus</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">global-config</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">db-config</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">id-type</span>: <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">auto</span> <span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">#使用数据库默认id自增策略</span></p><p>```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">**2.在实体类中使用注解</span><span style=\"color: #d69d85;font-weight: bold;\">`@TableId(value = &quot;id&quot;,type = IdType.AUTO)`</span><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">配置**</span></p><p><br/></p><p>```java</p><p><span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">//lombok</span></p><p>@<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Data</span> &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">// = @Getter+@Setter</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">public</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">class</span> <span style=\"color: #4ec9b0;\">Book</span> {</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; @<span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">TableId</span>(value <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">&quot;id&quot;</span>,type <span style=\"color: #b4b4b4;\">=</span> <span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">IdType</span>.<span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">AUTO</span>)</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">private</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">Integer</span> <span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">id</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">private</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">String</span> <span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">type</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">private</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">String</span> <span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">name</span>;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">private</span> <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">String</span> <span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;\">description</span>;</p><p>}</p><p>```</p><p><br/><br/><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">## </span><span style=\"color: #c8c8c8;font-weight: bold;\">四、开启Mybatis-plus日志</span></p><p><br/></p><p>mybatis-plus执行时，默认是不显示执行过程以及执行的sql语句的，这样调试时很是不方便，所以要打开日志功能</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">**在application.yml中开启mybatis-plus日志，设置日志显示方式为打印在控制台，配置代码如下：**</span></p><p><br/></p><p>```yaml</p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">mybatis-plus</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">global-config</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">db-config</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">id-type</span>: <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">auto</span> <span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">#使用数据库默认id自增策略</span></p><p>&nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">configuration</span>:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #569cd6;\">log-impl</span>: <span style=\"color: #d69d85;\">org.apache.ibatis.logging.stdout.StdOutImpl</span> &nbsp;<span style=\"color: #57a64a;\">#日志打印到控制台</span></p><p>```</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: #569cd6;font-weight: bold;\">**执行效果（显示完整的执行过程）：**</span></p><p><br/></p><p>```</p><p>Creating a new SqlSession</p><p>SqlSession [org.apache.ibatis.session.defaults.DefaultSqlSession@1e4c6583] was not registered for synchronization because synchronization is not active</p><p>JDBC Connection [com.mysql.cj.jdbc.ConnectionImpl@76fe6cdc] will not be managed by Spring</p><p>